OL,3,CCalls for designated waiting areas for
OL,4,Ccancer patients in A&E department
OL,6,FA north Wales woman is calling on
OL,7,FWales' largest health board to open
OL,8,Fdesignated safe spaces for cancer
OL,9,Fpatients forced to attend Accident and
OL,10,FEmergency departments.
OL,12,FDelia Lodge has gathered thousands of
OL,13,Fsignatures for her petition, set up to
OL,14,Fhelp patients like her daughter,
OL,15,FRebecca Quayle, who has terminal
OL,16,Fsecondary breast cancer. Rebecca is
OL,17,Fbeing treated at Ysbyty Glan Clwyd in
OL,18,FBodelwyddan, part of the Betsi
OL,19,FCadwaladr University Health Board.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/10
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
