OL,3,CCalls for designated waiting areas for
OL,4,Ccancer patients in A&E department
OL,6,FDelia and Rebecca have no complaints
OL,7,Fregarding the oncology care itself,
OL,8,Fbut problems arise if 41-year-old Mrs
OL,9,FQuayle falls ill out of hours. The
OL,10,Ffamily fears that picking up an
OL,11,Fillness on top of a compromised immune
OL,12,Fsystem "could technically kill" her.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/10
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
