CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F467A1775139066
OL,3,CCalls for designated waiting areas for
OL,4,Ccancer patients in A&E department
OL,6,FMrs Lodge, who has three adult
OL,7,Fdaughters, said: "I have a Facebook
OL,8,Fand paper petition because I want a
OL,9,Fcancer patient waiting area in the A&E
OL,10,Fdepartment. At the moment, if cancer
OL,11,Fpatients are ill in the evening or at
OL,12,Fthe weekend, they have to sit with the
OL,13,Fgeneral public in A&E, and I think
OL,14,Fthat should not happen. They need
OL,15,Fsomewhere they can sit in safety while
OL,16,Fthey are waiting to be seen."
OL,18,FShe added: "I'm not asking for
OL,19,Ffunding. No more doctors, no more
OL,20,Fnurses. Just one room."
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/10
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
