OL,3,CCalls for designated waiting areas for
OL,4,Ccancer patients in A&E department
OL,6,FRebecca, a mother of three, was
OL,7,Fdiagnosed with cancer four years ago.
OL,8,F"My journey started in November 2022
OL,9,Fwhen I started having chemo for
OL,10,Fprimary breast cancer," she said. "By
OL,11,F2023, I was technically told I was
OL,12,Fcured. Unfortunately, by 2024, I was
OL,13,Fclassed as terminal, with a recurrence
OL,14,Fin my lymph nodes and local spread as
OL,15,Fwell.
OL,17,F"I'm going through chemo at the
OL,18,Fmoment. Unfortunately, I've not got
OL,19,Fmany options left, but like my mother,
OL,20,Fyou can see I'm a fighter."
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/10
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
