OL,3,CCalls for designated waiting areas for
OL,4,Ccancer patients in A&E department
OL,6,FAs the cancer unit at Ysbyty Glan
OL,7,FClwyd is closed over the weekend,
OL,8,Fpatients must go through the A&E
OL,9,Fdepartment if they feel unwell. Mrs
OL,10,FLodge said this has happened to her
OL,11,Fdaughter on numerous occasions.
OL,13,F"Rebecca was ill with an infection in
OL,14,Fher chest wall; she went in at five in
OL,15,Fthe morning and they assessed her,
OL,16,Fthen sat her in the corridor. She
OL,17,Fwaited until quarter to nine in the
OL,18,Fevening before she went to the cancer
OL,19,Fward and was given a bed."
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/10
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
