PN,46706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F467A1775139066
OL,3,CCalls for designated waiting areas for
OL,4,Ccancer patients in A&E department
OL,6,FMrs Lodge said she was sitting in a
OL,7,Froom where the bins were "overflowing"
OL,8,Fand she felt "very angry". While she
OL,9,Fdoes not blame the staff and knows
OL,10,Fthey work hard, she is adamant that
OL,11,Fchange is needed.
OL,13,FRebecca, a former teacher from Kinmel
OL,14,FBay, is supporting her mother's
OL,15,Fpetition. "A&E, to be fair, is a
OL,16,Fbroken system. They do as much as they
OL,17,Fcan. There have been occasions where
OL,18,Fthey have found me a quieter place,
OL,19,Fbut unfortunately on others, like Mum
OL,20,Fwas saying, I've been on a corridor.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G6/10
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,468,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F467A1775139066
OL,3,CCalls for designated waiting areas for
OL,4,Ccancer patients in A&E department
OL,6,F"You know, people are throwing up next
OL,7,Fto you. You can hear Covid swabs
OL,8,Fcoming back positive and then (the
OL,9,Fpatients) get taken away. So it's a
OL,10,Fvery scary place to be. The bottom
OL,11,Fline is it could technically kill us.
OL,12,FThat's why Mum's so worried, I think."
OL,14,FRebecca admits there have been times
OL,15,Fwhen she has considered not attending
OL,16,FA&E due to safety fears, but has
OL,17,Falways ultimately followed medical
OL,18,Fadvice and gone.
OL,26,@pD@_pmqD@Ipn
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G7/10
