SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F467A1775139066
OL,3,CCalls for designated waiting areas for
OL,4,Ccancer patients in A&E department
OL,6,FIn a written statement, Betsi
OL,7,FCadwaladr Health Board said it fully
OL,8,Frecognises the concerns raised about
OL,9,Fimmunocompromised patients spending
OL,10,Ftime within emergency departments.
OL,12,FChris Lynes, Deputy Executive Director
OL,13,Fof Nursing & Midwifery for the board,
OL,14,Fadded: "Despite best efforts, there is
OL,15,Foften no appropriate space within or
OL,16,Fclose to Emergency Departments that
OL,17,Fcould safely be used as a separate
OL,18,Fwaiting area while still allowing
OL,19,Fstaff to closely monitor patients who
OL,20,Fmay become unwell.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G8/10
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,468,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46709
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F467A1775139066
OL,3,CCalls for designated waiting areas for
OL,4,Ccancer patients in A&E department
OL,6,F"Wherever possible, patients who are
OL,7,Fmore vulnerable to infection are
OL,8,Fprioritised for a cubicle. At the same
OL,9,Ftime, our teams must also balance the
OL,10,Fneeds of other vulnerable groups
OL,11,Fwithin the significant pressures our
OL,12,FEmergency Departments continue to
OL,13,Fface. While we are not currently able
OL,14,Fto implement the suggestion of a
OL,15,Fseparate designated area, we want to
OL,16,Freassure patients and families that
OL,17,Four teams are fully aware of these
OL,18,Fconcerns and remain committed to
OL,19,Fproviding safe, compassionate care."
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G9/10
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
