OL,3,CCalls for designated waiting areas for
OL,4,Ccancer patients in A&E department
OL,6,FThe response has been criticised by
OL,7,FMrs Lodge, who says she will continue
OL,8,Fto fight for her daughter and other
OL,9,Fcancer patients.
